      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit excels in throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and remains thermally efficient under load. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque vectoring. Critically, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary longitudinal stress points. The double-VANOS system has been recently recalibrated for peak variable valve timing. While the Estoril Blue finish shows minor road-wear, the suspension kinematics remain tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers. This is a purist\u2019s specimen optimized for turn-in precision and high-RPM linearity.",
